<span font-size="large"><b>nwg-shell v0.5.0</b> (2023.06.09)</span>

You may <b>add Hyprland support</b> to your current nwg-shell installation. To copy default configs for Hyprland, execute:

<i>$ nwg-shell-installer -r -hypr</i>

in your terminal emulator. Then install the `hyprland` package and enjoy.

Ah, yes: for nwg-displays to work on Hyprland, you'll also need the `wlr-randr` package!

